title: Worst meal of our lives. Went
text: Worst meal of our lives. Went into the club and ate at the ground floor cafe sunday lunchtime. I had big breakfast, my wife chicken schnitzel chips and salad. Very easy and would have thought very safe club food. It was a disgrace. The worst meal we have had anywhere in the world in our lifetime. Everything tasted of dirty oil. $35 down the drain. Would not go back ever again.

title: Great local Italian
text: My wife and I had a great lunch here last Sunday. The menu is substantially reduced due to covid but it was bulked up with a good specials offering. We had a pizza followed by two of the specials, a beautiful perch dish and a crab linguine. The food was perfection. The location is sensational. The staff friendly and efficient. The owner even stopped by for a chat and then served a complimentary limoncello which was near freezing deliciousness. Whilst this was not our first time at maldinis We will be back again

title: Perfection
text: What a fantastic place for a meal. The quality of food, presentation and pricing. Service is first class. Will certainly be back as soon as we can

title: Get take away pies every time we visit or pass by
text: This is one of the best pie shops in Sydney. Have been getting pies of differing varieties from here for years And they are always fantastic. Usually take away and reheat for dinner and they are just as good.

title: Best place to stop in Nabiac
text: Your detour off of the highway to have breakfast or lunch in this gem will not disappoint. We stop in here or the bakery each time we pass. The food is delicious. The staff very friendly and efficient. Well priced. You seriously could not ask for more

title: Perfect steak and ribs
text: Had a great lunch with my wife in here. Certainly the service was first class. Really good food choices that are well prepared and full of flavour. Priced as a good restaurant. Worth a visit

title: Great town centre
text: Come here when we are able to. Great atmosphere. Some great food choices. Good markets on many weekend. Really great place to take kids also

title: Really nice friendly local tavern
text: Had a weekend lunch in here with a group of 10. Food was really good, certainly not cheap by pub standards but the location justifies pricing. Good beers. Great staff. Location, location, location.

title: Really nice bistro meals .
text: My wife and I have eaten here on a number of occasions. Really great atmosphere, location , friendly service and great value bistro meals. Good choice of draft beers to go with it. Overall a good experience

title: Great new Marsden pub
text: Beautiful new hotel. Really great food selection. Great choice of local and boutique ales. One of the best pubs around in my opinion. A must if nearby

title: Maybe the best burger joint around
text: Wow, the food here is absolutely bloody fantastic. When you see the amount of people eating or waiting to eat it tells something. Have ate here mAny times and had beef, chicken and some specialty burgers and they are all fantastic. Great selection of chicken wings also. This place an absolute must

title: Really nice local club
text: Stopped in here whilst travelling with my son for a beer and quick lunch. Really nice club in one of the best locations possible. Great people. Really good food and beer and well priced. Great place if you happen to be nearby

title: Great location, better people
text: Stayed here in a single room when I went to see my Granddaughter start school. Really great people that are friendly and extremely helpful. Good coffee complimentary on site. Really good location. Rooms are clean, tidy and well equipped. A small motel that is certainly worthy of staying at.

title: Can’t go past without dropping in
text: What a great place. Being dropping in here for years and it never disappoints. Great pies, sausage rolls, cakes and coffees. Really friendly staff and the best village atmosphere bar none. A must when visiting or passing close by to Berrima.

title: What a simply fantastic pub
text: Really fantastic pub attached to the Mercure hotel. Fantastic atmosphere, great daily specials and food that is simply the best. Good choice of beers. Great location. Staff fantastic.. will be back

title: Great historic hotel
text: We stayed here for a couple of nights to do some tourist things around Canberra. Really great hotel, historic, beautiful large loft rooms, clean, comfortable, well priced and with great local staff. Attached pub has the best meals, great beer and really good atmosphere. This place is a gem.

title: Really great Italian at thelakeside
text: Really great Italian at the lakeside. Pizza here is excellent. Staff very efficient and courteous. Well priced and of high quality. Will eat here again when in BV AREA

title: The best burger
text: The burgers here have a solid reputation and once you visit you will understand why. The food here is just the best. Great location, atmosphere, staff, pricing. I cannot wait to return

title: Really great spot for breakfast
text: Really great spot for breakfast and lunch. High st location. Really good quality food, well priced and excellent staff. Certainly up there with the best cafes in the area

title: Great location, better price
text: Small motel in the heart of town. Clean, very tidy, good amenities, great location and very well priced. Staff were very helpful. Good off street parking. Restaurant on site as well as easy walk to dozens of other choices. Will use this place again for certain.

title: Best priced resort in Port
text: Went here with other family members during a family visit to Port. Great place on the Hastings river. Choice of waterfront cabins or motel. We chose cabins which were great. Clean, tidy, good pool area, kids playground and numerous picnic areas. Will be our choice of stay on lol future visits

title: My Port favoutite
text: Just love this restaurant for breakfast, lunch or dinner. Such great food choice. Never had a bad meal free so many visits. Great staff. Well priced. Great variety. Just love it.

title: Beautiful walk and location
text: One of the most popular attractions in port. Really beautiful walk from town out along the break wall. So much to see and read with all of the brightly decorated boulders. Have to do this every time we go and visit family.

title: Great local italian
text: This is a gem in western Sydney. Really great Italian food. Very well priced. Convenient shopping centre location, very good staff. Really great pizza, pastas, seafood. A must try when in Penrith.

title: Great food, better location
text: One of the best lunch locations this side of the harbour,.really popular weekend spot. Great food, wonderful views, well priced with great staff. One of our go to lunch spots

title: Great bistro meals
text: This is such a great place to get a really good steak, burger, fish n chips and a large variety of other good bistro type feeds. Well priced, clean and tidy and really food staff. A good choice when in Liverpool.

title: Great club cafe. Really good
text: Great club cafe. Really good menu, fresh food that is well priced. Numerous other choices as well including pizza (delicious), noodle bar, desert bar and others. Certainly worthwhile if you are heading past and want a good meal

title: Great new zoo
text: This is a really great place to take a young family for the day out. Well laid out, flat and everything easy access. Good aquarium and reptile/nocturnal house. Great pic in areas as well as a number of restaurants, cafes. Really worth a visit

title: Great local restaurant
text: Saw these guys calling out for support on Facebook following the closedown of the restaurant and cafe industry. Thought it should be supported so tried it out for a take away pizza. The service is first class. The pizza up there with the best available locally. Please do give your support to this business so that we may all enjoy dining in somewhere in the near future.

title: Perfection
text: Wow, this restaurant, meal quality, service, staff just about perfection. We had steak and fish along with entrees and wine and they were the absolute best. Well done the garden

title: Fantastic burgers
text: Staying down the road from here so we used it a couple of times for a simple dinner. Food is very generous, tasty and well priced. Delicious burgers and fries. Very good staff and location

title: Perfect coffee
text: As we were staying in the hotel this was the perfect place for a great coffee each morning. Staff very friendly and efficient. Best coffee in the area.

title: Upgrade the room
text: Night one we were in a room that was so small and had air conditioning that sounded like we were on a runway. We spoke to reception and paid to upgrade to a much better room. Great location, great staff, good bedding and bathroom. Will return

title: Just love Denny’s
text: As we were staying just down the road we ate here a number of times. We missed Denny’s from when we had it in Oz and it is still very good. Fresh, well priced and beautiful staff

title: Great beer and dinner
text: Had dinner in here twice whilst in Waikiki. Really great food choices, icy cold beer and great service. A good choice whilst in Waikiki

title: Great breakfast joint
text: This is certainly worth the wait in the queue for one of the best breakfasts on the island. Great staff, beautiful food and reasonably priced

title: A must in Waikiki
text: Been here many times and it is always a worthwhile trip. Heaps of major brands and major discounts over retail. Lots of transport options and food choices

title: HUUUUGE
text: This would have to be one of the largest shopping malls in the world, it is huge and I think impossible to get around it all. Plenty of global brands, eating options. Worth a visit

title: Popular monument
text: Ver popular spot, particularly for our Asian friends. Good photo opportunity at the best beach location. I am sure that it is visited by everyone that comes to Waikiki

title: Fantastic zoo
text: Whilst we have been to Hawaii a number of times this was a first going to the zoo and it didn’t disappoint. Great people, excellent facilities and assortment of exotic animals. A really great alternative to the beach

title: Happening place
text: One of the worlds best seaside locations with the one exception of all of the homeless utilising all of the public areas. Sadly this is the world we live in I guess. Other than that this is simply a great place

title: A world of burgers
text: Great burger concept with burgers representing countries around the world. Really great quality, well priced and generous serving. Great staff and very clean and tidy

title: The best burger
text: One of the best burgers I think we have ever experienced. We had these accompanied by fries and onion rings which were delicious as well as icy cold beer and wine. Great location and superbly friendly staff

title: The best chicken
text: Gotta love Frango. Very consistently good. Well priced delicious food and excellent staff. Why would anyone eat kfc when you want chicken

title: Great steaks
text: Had a simple Christmas gathering with some work colleagues here at end December. Was really great food, steaks delicious, pizza and bruschetta divine. Great location and excellent staff

title: Simple breakfast
text: Had quick breakfast of bacon and eggs on sourdough and coffees whilst shopping. Nice meal that was quickly and freshly prepared and quite tasty. Nice staff and well priced

title: Nice coldy
text: Great spot to grab a really cold beverage on a very hot south coast day. Really good pub. Great staff. Lots of tap beers, good bistro. Best pub in town

title: Very nice berry motel
text: Stayed here for a couple of nights whilst visiting berry, Kiama areas. Really nice little motel, very clean and well appointed. Owner is very pleasant and occupying. Very good bedding, bathroom and cold air con. Certainly will not disappoint

title: Best seafood lunch
text: Had one of the best cafe seafood lunches in here that we have ever had. We had flathead and the seafood basket, both were divine. Great location, excellent staff. Will be back anytime in the area

title: Very ordinary Italian
text: More like an Italian fast food joint than a restaurant charging $40 plus for a main. This used to be a great restaurant but no more. Poor staff, expensive, ordinary fare. Over it now.

title: Delicious breakfast
text: We regularly use the cafe as it is such great value whilst being very good quality. Really great service from friendly staff and huge portion sizes. One of the best club meals around

title: Great club meals
text: Great location, excellent staff and really great quality food. Serve sizes are impressive as is the cost. A really great choice for a nice club lunch

title: Nice place for the grandkids
text: Been going here since I was a kid. A lot has changed to say the least but it is such a great place to take kids. Lots of local wildlife, great resting areas and friendly staff. Perfect

title: Good breakfast spot
text: Nice place for a well prepared and tasty simple hot breakfast with a good cup of coffee. Pricing is good, quality is good, staff are excellent. Worthy of a look

title: Very nice local Italian
text: Had a lunch business meal in here and was very impressed with the quality, service, pricing and spectacular location. The better of the local Italians

title: Best value pub lunch in town
text: Go in here regularly for a steak and a beer. Has to be the best value pub meal in town. Good portion size, good service and nice venue.

title: Best burger in town
text: Beefys never ever disappoints. Great quality, well priced, delicious burgers. Staff are friendly, restaurant clean and tidy. Gotta give it a go

title: Great brunch spot
text: Rightly so one of the highest rated restaurants in the PENRITH area. The food here is sensational as is the service and ambience. Will be back

title: Best chicken bar none
text: Had chicken and chips from the PENRITH outlet and if they are all as good then this would have to be the best fried chicken in Oz. Simply perfect

title: OMG the noise
text: Went here for a special meal on a Friday night. Food was not too bad. Service was good. I know it was a very busy night but have to say i have never been to a louder restaurant in my life.
